<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870522-0047 </DOCNO><HL> Bessemer Group IncreasesStake in Intermedics Inc.</HL><DD> 05/22/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> ITMTENDER OFFERS, MERGERS, ACQUISITIONS (TNM) </IN><DATELINE> WASHINGTON  </DATELINE><TEXT>   A group including Bessemer Securities Corp. raised its stake in Intermedics Inc. to 18.8% of the common shares outstanding.    In a Securities and Exchange Commission filing, the group said it holds 1,934,200 Intermedics shares, including 128,000 shares purchased from April 14 to May 20 at $19.75 to $23.50 each. According to the filing, the shares were purchased as an investment.    Bessemer Securities is based in New York. Intermedics is an Angleton, Texasbased maker of medical products. </TEXT></DOC>